	<p>Prerequisites: <CourseLink id={1650} href="/EDS#289B">EDS 289B</CourseLink>, and Joint EdD in Educational Leadership student status or consent of instructor.</p>
</CourseCard>
<CourseCard id="289D" shortName="EDS 289D" longName="Dissertation Writing Seminar" units="4" url="/EDS#289D">
